        "description": "Our sincere effort to spread warmth to those in need during the harsh winter.",
        "content": "<h3>Program Details</h3><p class='editor-paragraph editor-empty'></p><div data-youtube-video=\"\"><iframe class=\"editor-youtube-video\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" autoplay=\"false\" disablekbcontrols=\"false\" enableiframeapi=\"false\" endtime=\"0\" ivloadpolicy=\"0\" loop=\"false\" modestbranding=\"true\" origin=\"\" playlist=\"\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fhJO634H1Hw\" start=\"0\"></iframe></div><p class=\"editor-paragraph editor-empty\"></p><p class='editor-paragraph'>Those of us who live in cities or are relatively well-off barely feel the impact of winter. The cold doesn't seep through our brick walls, and for many, winter is simply a time for stylish outfits. But for many poor villagers, winter is a season of fear—a time when they cannot even provide warm clothing for their children. It becomes a season of sorrow and helplessness.</p><p class='editor-paragraph editor-empty'></p><p class='editor-paragraph'>To deliver warm clothes to such vulnerable people, As-Sunnah Foundation organizes winter clothing distribution every year.</p>",
